## cache-line-size\n\n**Source:** Linux kernel Documentation\n\n```\n- cache-line-size : Size of L2 cache lines

Example:

	L2: l2-cache-controller@20000 {
		compatible = "fsl,bsc9132-l2-cache-controller", "cache";
		reg = <0x20000 0x1000>;
		cache-line-size = <32>; // 32 bytes
		cache-size = <0x40000>; // L2,256K
		interrupts = <16 2 1 0>;
	};\n```
